Dialogue: 5,0:27:47.10,0:27:49.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chama-se Casa Franky.
Dialogue: 5,0:27:52.71,0:27:54.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:55.59,0:27:57.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:58.47,0:28:03.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sério, quando não tem como ele achar o Usopp sozinho...!}O\Nque dá? Como se ele pudesse fugir e encontrar o Usopp sozinho!
