Dialogue: 5,0:29:24.07,0:29:25.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma multidão de pessoas...
Dialogue: 5,0:29:25.80,0:29:28.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espere, {Y}yagara-{\i1}chan{\fs15} {r}!  Pare!  Pare!{\fs\i0\i0}
