Dialogue: 5,0:29:39.00,0:29:40.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!  Acordar!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:40.38,0:29:42.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!  Você está bem?!
