Dialogue: 5,0:30:01.49,0:30:05.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim... {Porque eu sou fraco.} Eu era muito fraco.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:06.61,0:30:08.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Essa grande quantidade de dinheiro...} Todo esse dinheiro...
Dialogue: 5,0:30:08.30,0:30:10.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,eles roubaram tudo.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:12.50,0:30:14.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 5,0:30:14.01,0:30:15.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim?
